title: Weather on the 8s
description:
Ted Lancaster and Mary Day bring you the Channel 6 Evening News, featuring Weather on the 8s: bringing you your local weather, every 8 seconds.

Presented by Gramps

Written by Jesse Acini

Featuring Noah Plener, Elaine Carroll, Eddie Dunn, Abbi Crutchfield, Jesse Acini, and Rory Panagotopulos

Directed by Alden Ford
